==English==

===Noun===
'''bowleg'''
#A leg that curve outward at the knee. It might refer to the leg of a human, animal or even a piece of furniture. For humans this deformity is formally called [[genu varum]].

===Adjective===
'''bow-legged''' (more bow-legged, most bow-legged)
#Having legs that curve outward at the knees, having bowlegs.

==== Synonyms ====
#[[bandy]], [[bandy-legged]]
#[[genu varum]], [[tibia vara]], [[valgus]] deformity

